finalPattern.pattern_name: Titles that frame breaking tech/government developments as an imminent end-times threat and add an urgent, list-like escape directive (e.g., “Escape These Countries… NEW DIGITAL MARK”) drive materially higher TPS vs the channel’s devotional baseline.

evidence.title: Escape These Countries When They Introduce This NEW DIGITAL MARK!
evidence.excerpt: Outperformed typical devotional uploads; stacks prophecy keyword + urgency + list-like promise.
